Package: IGCM
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-08-02
Title: Invariant Generalized Covariance Measure 
Description: Invariant generalized covariance measure (I-GCM) integrates flexible machine learning method with the principle of invariant causal prediction to identify direct causal variables for a given outcome variable in high-dimensional settings.
